#
# Documentation: K*0 forced to K+ pi-, D~0 forced to pi+ pi- pi+ pi-, 
#                Phase Space model for D decay,
#                Only favoured mode for B->DK* (SVS model)
# EndDocumentation
#
# PhysicsWG: B2OC
# CPUTime: <1 min
