Alias MyK*0      K*0
Alias Myanti-K*0 anti-K*0
ChargeConj MyK*0 Myanti-K*0
Alias      Myanti-D0   anti-D0
Alias      MyD0        D0
ChargeConj MyD0        Myanti-D0
#
Decay B0sig
  # SVS model
  1.000    MyK*0      Myanti-D0   SVS;  
Enddecay 
CDecay anti-B0sig
#
# PhaseSpace model in D0 decay
Decay MyD0
  1.000    pi+        pi-         pi+         pi-          PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-D0
#
Decay MyK*0
  1.000    K+         pi-         VSS;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-K*0
#
End
